imageAssets.description: A subtle, abstract background image for a web theremin. Style: digital art, light theme. Dominant colors: very light greys (e.g., #F0F5FA, #E8EFF5), soft blues (e.g., #D0E0FF, #C0D8F8), and hints of silver. The design should evoke sound waves, gentle electronic circuits, or ethereal patterns. It should be non-distracting and provide a clean, modern, technological feel. Avoid strong contrasts or overly busy elements. Overall mood: calm, focused, slightly futuristic. Ensure it tiles seamlessly if possible, or is large enough to cover common aspect ratios without obvious repetition if not tiling.
imageAssets.purpose: Background for the main theremin interaction area (#thereminZone) to enhance visual appeal without distracting from controls. It will be applied using `background-image` CSS property.

imageAssets.description: Icon: Sine wave symbol. Style: clean, minimalist line art icon, single solid color (intended to be #0d6efd Bootstrap primary blue, or a color that works well on a light button background). Clearly depicts one or two cycles of a smooth sine wave. Optimized for use as a small icon on a button (e.g., 24x24 or 32x32 effective display size). Background should be transparent.
imageAssets.purpose: Visual icon for the 'Sine' waveform selection button in the control panel. Path: /generated_images/waveform_sine.png

imageAssets.description: Icon: Square wave symbol. Style: clean, minimalist line art icon, single solid color (intended to be #0d6efd Bootstrap primary blue). Clearly depicts one or two cycles of a sharp square wave. Optimized for use as a small icon on a button. Background should be transparent.
imageAssets.purpose: Visual icon for the 'Square' waveform selection button in the control panel. Path: /generated_images/waveform_square.png

imageAssets.description: Icon: Sawtooth wave symbol. Style: clean, minimalist line art icon, single solid color (intended to be #0d6efd Bootstrap primary blue). Clearly depicts one or two cycles of a ramp-like sawtooth wave. Optimized for use as a small icon on a button. Background should be transparent.
imageAssets.purpose: Visual icon for the 'Sawtooth' waveform selection button in the control panel. Path: /generated_images/waveform_sawtooth.png

imageAssets.description: Icon: Triangle wave symbol. Style: clean, minimalist line art icon, single solid color (intended to be #0d6efd Bootstrap primary blue). Clearly depicts one or two cycles of a symmetrical triangle wave. Optimized for use as a small icon on a button. Background should be transparent.
imageAssets.purpose: Visual icon for the 'Triangle' waveform selection button in the control panel. Path: /generated_images/waveform_triangle.png
